query:
SELECT
                  r.created,
                  COALESCE(m.name, v.version_number, u.username, 'unknown') "title!"
                FROM reports r
                LEFT JOIN mods m ON r.mod_id = m.id
                LEFT JOIN versions v ON r.version_id = v.id
                LEFT JOIN users u ON r.user_id = u.id
                WHERE r.id = $1
